nodes.text: Dorus Pyne was a male Human living during the Cold War. He resided on Tatooine in 3643 BBY.
Dorus Pyne appears in the game files for Star Wars: The Old Republic under npc.location.tatooine.bronze.republic.the_hunted category. He does not appear during Tatooine quest "The Hunted".
